<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0005179> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Also consider annotating to 'receptor agonist activity ; GO:0048018'." .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0005179> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hormone activity" .
