_:B0c202148002e23e534c4a4493443a0e0 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedTarget> "Either of a pair of glandular pouches that lie one on either side of the male reproductive tract posterolateral to the urinary bladder and in the human male secrete a sugar- and protein-containing fluid into the ejaculatory duct." .
_:B0c202148002e23e534c4a4493443a0e0 <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "BTO:0001234" .
